      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YACHT CHOICE (2) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 0.9 lengths (25.02) behind Ruadhans Boy at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Key chance in this line up. RANGEY LADY (6) missed the frame two runs back then won at her latest appearance by one length at this track over 400m (24.97). Levels up but can win again with the confidence restored. CATUNDA NEMO (5) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 6th and beaten 6 lengths at this track (25.44). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. AINT GOT NO CASH (1) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
